Mimi Benzell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mimi_Benzell 0 Miriam Ruth "Mimi" Benzell (April 6, 1918 – December 23, 1970) was an American soprano who performed with the Metropolitan Opera before establishing herself as a Broadway musical theatre, television, and nightclub performer.
